    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Bank Woori Saudara Indonesia 1906 Tbk provides various commercial banking products and services for individuals and businesses in Indonesia. It operates through six segments: Pensioner; Employee; Commercial; Treasury; Funding; and Others. The company offers current and savings accounts; time and demand deposits; commercial, pension/retirement, employee general, mortgage, corporate, and car loans, as well as loans for micro, small, and medium enterprises; and bank guarantees. It also provides wealth management; treasury products comprising foreign exchange (forex), money market, fixed income, and update information services on currency exchange rates; and payment services through automatic teller machines and digital banking channels. In addition, the company offers remittance forex transfer and collection; fund transfer; bancassurance; international banking; export and import; safe deposit box; trade finance; Internet and mobile banking; state revenue; and electronic data capture services. Further, it invests in placements and securities. The company was founded in 1906 and is headquartered in Jakarta, Indonesia. PT Bank Woori Saudara Indonesia 1906 Tbk is a subsidiary of Woori Bank.",
